Images: ["[630_360_16806...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680628552-4032.jpeg)", "[1680628552-67...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680628552-6793.jpeg)", "[1680628552-70...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680628552-7096.jpeg)"]

